substep.action:
Parse the script's stdout. Confirm:
- Three paths returned, all under {{session.shared_folder}}/tickets/{{session.slug}}/
- Each file exists on disk and is non-empty
- Each file's frontmatter parses as YAML
- Each file's `kind:` matches expected (ticket / research / questions)

Run `thoughts validate {{ticket_path}}` and confirm zero validation
errors. If validation fails, halt and surface the errors to the user —
the bundle is malformed and ticket-grill should not start.

Store in session:
- {{session.ticket_path}}
- {{session.research_path}}
- {{session.questions_path}}
- {{session.worklog_path}}
- {{session.bundle_dir}}
